  "description": {
   "en": "Hatori, a high school teacher leading an ordinary life, notices one day that his student, Spica Tsumugi, is being bullied. On a rainy day after school, Hatori finds himself alone with Tsumugi by chance. \n\nHatori tells her, \"I'll do something about it!\" but Tsumugi gently takes his hand and says with a smile, \"Hatori-sensei, you're such a liar.\" \n\nTeacher and student… two people who should not get too close. This somewhat bewitching girl will dramatically change Hatori's ordinary life."
  },
